**Why This Is Dangerous**:
- Client-side checks can be bypassed by directly calling API endpoints
- Attackers can modify JavaScript, localStorage, or cookies to fake admin status
- No authentication/authorization verification on sensitive endpoints
- The 2021 Parler breach used similar flaws to download 70TB of data

